    "question": "The number of elements in the set $S = \\left\\{ (r, k) : k \\in \\mathbb{Z} \\text{ and } {}^{36}C_{r+1} = \\frac{6 \\left({}^{35}C_r\\right)}{k^2 - 3} \\right\\}$, is :",
