    "question": "The number of critical points of the function $f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\left| \\frac{\\sin x}{x} \\right|, & x \\neq 0 \\\\ 1, & x = 0 \\end{cases}$ in the interval $(-2\\pi, 2\\pi)$ is equal to :",
