    "question": "If the domain of the function $f(x) = \\sqrt{\\log_{(0.6)} \\left( \\frac{2x - 5}{x^2 - 4} \\right)}$ is $(-\\infty, a] \\cup \\{b\\} \\cup [c, d) \\cup (e, \\infty)$, then the value of $a + b + c + d + e$ is _______.",
