    "question": "![Capacitor half-filled with dielectric](https://www.sarthaks.com/?qa=blob&qa_blobid=12716304422748890071)\nA parallel plate air capacitor has a capacitance $C$. When it is half filled as show in figure with a dielectric constant $K = 5$, the percentage increase in the capacitance is _______.",
