    "question": "![Two mutually perpendicular dipoles](https://cracku.in/media/uploads/image_ym0nAW9.png)\nTwo short electric dipoles $A$ and $B$ having dipole moment $p_1$ and $p_2$ respectively are placed with their axis mutually perpendicular as shown in the figure. The resultant electric field at a point $x$ is making an angle of $60^\\circ$ with the line joining points $O$ and $x$. The ratio of the dipole moments $p_2/p_1$ is _______.",
