    "question": "Let $A = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 & 2 \\ -2 & 0 & 1 \\ 1 & 3 & 5 \\end{bmatrix}$. Then the sum of all elements of the matrix $\\text{adj}(\\text{adj}(2(\\text{adj} A)^{-1}))$ is equal to:",
