    "question": "Let $f$ be a real polynomial of degree $n$ such that $f(x) = f'(x)f''(x)$, for all $x \\in \\mathbb{R}$. If $f(0) = 0$, then $36 \\left( f'(2) + f''(2) + \\int_0^2 f(x) dx \\right)$ is equal to:",
