    "question": "Let $\\int_{-2}^{2} (|\\sin x| + [x \\sin x]) dx = 2(3 - \\cos 2) + \\beta$, where $[\\cdot]$ is the greatest integer function. Then $\\beta \\sin \\left( \\frac{\\beta}{2} \\right)$ equals:",
