    "question": "Let $y = y(x)$ be the solution of the differential equation $\\frac{dy}{dx} = (1 + x + x^2)(1 - y + y^2)$, $y(0) = \\frac{1}{2}$. Then $(2y(1) - 1)$ is equal to:",
