    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "question": "Let $\\vec{a}_k = (\\tan \\theta_k)\\hat{i} + \\hat{j}$ and $\\vec{b}_k = \\hat{i} - (\\cot \\theta_k)\\hat{j}$, where $\\theta_k = \\frac{2^{k-1}\\pi}{2^n + 1}$, for some $n \\in \\mathbb{N}, n > 5$. Then the value of $\\frac{\\sum_{k=1}^n |\\vec{a}_k|^2}{\\sum_{k=1}^n |\\vec{b}_k|^2}$ is \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_.",
