    "question": "The pH of a solution obtained by mixing $5$ mL of $0.1$ M $NH_4OH$ solution with $250$ mL of $0.1$ M $NH_4Cl$ solution is \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_ $\\times 10^{-2}$. (Nearest integer)\nGiven: $pK_b(NH_4OH) = 4.74$, $\\log 2 = 0.30$, $\\log 3 = 0.48$, $\\log 5 = 0.70$",
